{
  "stem": "19550.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You started out at the corner with the Jewish delicatessen store and the Jewish grocery store.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then came the Beta Midrash.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then came the central synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then came the lower classes of the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of, of the cheder.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then came the rabbi's residence with his synagogue and-- which also served as the yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then you came to the, the Jewish bakery.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then you came to the mikra.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then you came from the mikra.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You went to the [? close. ?] And then you went to the-- or in, in the same backyard, you had the, the scribes and his family.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And after that, you had the Jewish [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] counsel's office.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you had the, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the office of the beadles, who, by the way, were also collecting the taxes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's very interesting-- the system was quite interesting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I, I don't know whether it's really familiar, you know, in North America at all or to North Americans because it's never existed in North America.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You were assessed tax.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And you could, in effect, elect to pay the tax, either in installment or in one fell swoop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But by and large, most people would pay their tax by going to the beadle's home, who had a little window like a teller's window.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And you would buy a ticket to have your chicken slaughtered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thought I have to stop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that ticket not only permitted you to have your chickens slaughtered, but at the same time, constituted a payment towards your taxes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, in the backyard almost next to the-- to the [? close, ?] there was the slaughterhouse for the chicken.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
